riority access.\n6. Calculate/record:\n- total bandwidth generated based on a sigmoidal production function of group investment,\n- the number of files downloaded by each participant,\n- investment decisions of each participant in each round,\n- calculate earnings based on files downloaded plus tokens not invested.\n7. Estimate hierarchical linear models of investment behaviour accounting for individual and group-level variance.",
